602
00:35:53,701 --> 00:35:56,736
hello, daddy.

603
00:35:56,804 --> 00:35:58,705
Hello.

604
00:36:02,211 --> 00:36:04,713
- 9:00 tomorrow night.
- Where's the baby?

605
00:36:04,780 --> 00:36:07,249
I had Carla take him.
You weren't going to.

606
00:36:07,317 --> 00:36:09,651
- Henry and I have plans.
- I'd like to see him.

607
00:36:12,322 --> 00:36:14,356
- Hello, don.
- Henry.

608
00:36:14,424 --> 00:36:17,225
Come on, let's go.

609
00:36:34,877 --> 00:36:36,745
Garage door.

610
00:36:41,651 --> 00:36:45,220
