627
00:39:07,766 --> 00:39:09,734
Oh.

628
00:39:09,801 --> 00:39:12,103
It's almost 10:00.

629
00:39:12,171 --> 00:39:14,939
- I thought you said 10:00.
- She didn't.

630
00:39:15,007 --> 00:39:16,641
I've waited for you
plenty of times.

631
00:39:16,709 --> 00:39:19,577
Henry, do you mind?

632
00:39:19,645 --> 00:39:22,714
- Betty?
- It's okay.

633
00:39:22,782 --> 00:39:24,583
Does that mean I should stay
or not stay?

634
00:39:24,650 --> 00:39:25,918
Stay.

635
00:39:29,756 --> 00:39:31,990
When are you moving out?

636
00:39:32,058 --> 00:39:33,992
I don't know.

637
00:39:34,060 --> 00:39:35,561
