a little bit more about
the image of this agency.

672
00:41:41,790 --> 00:41:44,525
Well, nobody knows
about the ham stunt,

673
00:41:44,593 --> 00:41:48,430
So our image remains
pretty much where
you left it.

674
00:41:48,498 --> 00:41:51,700
I won't need you in
the Jantzen presentation.

675
00:41:51,768 --> 00:41:54,569
- Now you're being spiteful.
- No.

676
00:41:54,637 --> 00:41:57,205
I just think it would
be better not to have
a girl in the room.

677
00:42:00,910 --> 00:42:02,777
You know something?

678
00:42:02,845 --> 00:42:04,679
We are all here because of you.

679
00:42:06,582 --> 00:42:08,850
All we want to do
is please you.

680
00:42:18,459 --> 00:42:20,359
Why don't I put them
in the pantry?

681
00:42:20,427 --> 00:42:22,261
Christmas is around the corner.

682
00:42:22,329 --> 00:42:25,464
<i>Put them in the basement.</i>

683
00:42:25,532 --> 00:42:28,027
Did the children
like their gifts?

684
00:42:28,095 --> 00:42:29,695
They did.

685
00:42:33,066 --> 00:42:36,035
It's nice the holiday is
memorable in some other way.

686
00:42:36,103 --> 00:42:39,205
I'm sorry a little girl
spoiled your Thanksgiving.

687
00:42:39,978 --> 00:42:41,379
Next time I'll tell her
not to get sick.

688
00:42:41,414 --> 00:42:43,531
I've raised children
in my life, Henry.

689
00:42:43,599 --> 00:42:45,900
They're terrified of her.

690
00:42:45,968 --> 00:42:48,302
You don't know
any of the people
you're talking about.

691
00:42:48,370 --> 00:42:50,304
Well, I know
what you see in her.

692
