695
00:42:59,648 --> 00:43:01,782
Honestly, Henry,

696
00:43:01,850 --> 00:43:04,385
I don't know how you can stand
living in that man's dirt.

697
00:43:13,328 --> 00:43:15,596
<i>You go to the swimming pool,
you go to the beach,</i>

698
00:43:15,664 --> 00:43:17,932
<i>Take off your robe,
you head into the cabana.</i>

699
00:43:18,000 --> 00:43:22,142
